values.label: Drop charge
values.comment: Fee charged when a rental is terminated in a city or location other than where the rental originated.

values.label: Extra day
values.comment: The associated charge is for each day beyond the indicated base period.

values.label: Extra week
values.comment: The associated charge is for each week beyond the indicated base period.

values.label: Extra hour
values.comment: The associated charge is for each hour beyond the indicated base period.

values.label: Extra month
values.comment: The associated charge is for each month beyond the indicated base period.

values.label: Per mile
values.comment: The associated charge is for each mile the service is in use.

values.label: Per kilometer
values.comment: The associated charge is for each kilometer the service is in use.

values.label: Free miles
values.comment: To indicate there is no charge for the specified number of free miles.

values.label: Free kilometers
values.comment: To indicate there is no charge for the specified number of free kilometers.

values.label: Small contained animal
values.comment: The associated tariff is per animal up to the size of a domestic cat, stalled in suitable containers such as a cage, box or basket.
